  "text": "Previous work has noted that the synchronous update rules is unrealistic, and explored the effects of introducing random variation in the update times [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . Unlike that work, our speed-independent model has no concept of probability; it answers whether every possible timing of reactions results in a successful cell cycle.",
